pullrequest.title: Move files not ported to v1 to a separate dir for clarity

content.raw:
A few tests fail for me, not sure if that is expected.

1. `UNIT_WorldControl_TEST`

```
[Dbg] [Application.cc:87] Initializing application.
[GUI] [Dbg] [Application.cc:395] Create main window
[GUI] [Msg] Loading plugin [WorldControl]
[GUI] [Err] [Application.cc:361] Failed to load plugin [WorldControl] : couldn't get interface [ignition::rendering::v1::OgreRenderEnginePlugin].
/data/ignition/ign-gui/src/plugins/WorldControl_TEST.cc:43: Failure
Value of: app.LoadPlugin("WorldControl")
  Actual: false
Expected: true
/data/ignition/ign-gui/src/plugins/WorldControl_TEST.cc:51: Failure
Expected equality of these values:
  plugins.size()
    Which is: 0
  1
Segmentation fault (core dumped)
```

2. `UNIT_WorldStats_TEST`

```
[ RUN      ] WorldStatsTest.Load
[Dbg] [Application.cc:87] Initializing application.
[GUI] [Dbg] [Application.cc:395] Create main window
[GUI] [Msg] Loading plugin [WorldStats]
[GUI] [Err] [Application.cc:361] Failed to load plugin [WorldStats] : couldn't get interface [ignition::rendering::v1::OgreRenderEnginePlugin].
/data/ignition/ign-gui/src/plugins/WorldStats_TEST.cc:43: Failure
Value of: app.LoadPlugin("WorldStats")
  Actual: false
Expected: true
/data/ignition/ign-gui/src/plugins/WorldStats_TEST.cc:51: Failure
Expected equality of these values:
  plugins.size()
    Which is: 0
  1
Segmentation fault (core dumped)
```
